Season(summer).
Season(fall).
Season(winter).

# Define the students

Student(james).

# Emma's favorite season is summer

# Mia's favorite season is not the same as Emma's.

# All students who want to have a long vacation love summer.

Loves(james, summer).

∀x ∀s (FavoriteSeason(x, s) → Loves(x, s)).

# Conclusion:
FavoriteSeason(james, fall)

HasSeason(year1, fall)
